 jaundice.', 'Synergism', 'Felodipine, Amlodipine, Verapamil, Bisoprolol, Hydrochlorothiazide, Indapamide', 'Fluorouracil, Pemetrexed, Mercaptopurine, Cladribine, Trifluridine, Floxuridine, Gemcitabine, Nelarabine, Pralatrexate, Fludarabine, Decitabine, More', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/15067/', '[1] "Product Information. Clolar (clofarabine)." sanofi-aventis, Bridgewater, NJ.', 1767369485);
