nd jaundice.', 'Synergism', 'Fluorouracil, Pemetrexed, Mercaptopurine, Cladribine, Trifluridine, Floxuridine, Gemcitabine, Nelarabine, Cytarabine, Pralatrexate, Fludarabine, More', 'Romiplostim, Avatrombopag, Emicizumab, Coagulation factor VIIa Recombinant Human, Coagulation factor X human, Lusutrombopag, Anti-inhibitor coagulant complex, Antihemophilic factor, human recombinant, Fibrinogen human, Epinephrine, Coagulation Factor IX Human', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/15307/', '[1] "Product Information. Clolar (clofarabine)." sanofi-aventis, Bridgewater, NJ.', 1767369485);
